        <div class="content">
            <h2>Our Policy</h2>
            <br>
            <h3>At NileWay Rentals, transparency and customer trust are at the heart of our policies.</h3>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="second">
        <h1>We’re committed to providing you with a safe and transparent rental experience throughout Egypt!</h1>
       
    </div>

    <div class="All-cards">

        <div class="Cards-container">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="public/images/age-limit.png" alt="House Icon">
                    <h3>Age</h3>
                    <br>
                    <p>Renters must be at least 21 years old. Certain vehicles may require drivers to be 25+.</p>
                   
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="public/images/payment-method.png" alt="Phone Icon">
                    <h3>Payment</h3>
                    <br>
                    <p>All major credit/debit cards are accepted. A <strong>security deposit</strong> is required and will be held during the rental period.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="public/images/drivers-license.png" alt="Mail Icon">
                    <h3>License</h3>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>A valid Egyptian driver’s license or an international driver’s permit (IDP) is required.</p>
                    
            </div>

             <div class="card">
                <img src="public/images/cancel.png" alt="Mail Icon">
                    <h3>Free cancellations</h3>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>up to 24 hours before pickup, Late cancellations or no-shows may incur a fee up to <strong>1 day’s rental</p>
                    
            </div>
        </div>
